	"readme": "# PostCSS Japanese Stylesheets [![CI](https://github.com/ikkou/postcss-japanese-stylesheets/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/ikkou/postcss-japanese-stylesheets/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n\n[PostCSS] plugin for writing Japanese Stylesheets, especially for Japanese Traditional Colors.\n\n[PostCSS]: https://github.com/postcss/postcss\n\n## Input\n\n```css\n.foo {\n  背景: 肌色 !重要;\n  幅: 300px;\n  高さ: 200px;\n}\n\n.bar {\n  色: 暗黒色;\n  行揃え: 中央寄せ;\n  太さ: 太い;\n  行高: 1.6;\n}\n```\n\n## Output\n\n```css\n.foo {\n  background: #fce2c4 !important;\n  width: 300px;\n  height: 200px;\n}\n\n.bar {\n  color: #16160e;\n  text-align: center;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nInstall PostCSS and this plugin:\n\n```sh\nnpm install postcss postcss-japanese-stylesheets\n```\n\n```js\npostcss([ require('postcss-japanese-stylesheets') ])\n```\n\nSee [PostCSS] docs for examples for your environment.\n\n## Development\n\n```sh\nnpm install\nnpm test\n```\n\n## Thanks to\n\nInspiration from [postcss-russian-stylesheets](https://github.com/Semigradsky/postcss-russian-stylesheets)\n",
